node.text:
Exciting news today: Planners are back in stock, AND our 2022 calendars are officially available through the link in my bio! ✨

- Our planner (our FIRST ever planner!) has stickers, colorful comics, storage pocket, 16 months of planning pages, and all sorts of other good stuff. 

- Our desk calendar has HUNDREDS of comics for daily smiles, and it features 50 comics that were not in last year's daily calendar. 

- And our wall calendar has twelve of our FAVORITE comics, all colorized and ready to brighten up your wall. 

You can choose your fighter through the link in our bio! And to my passionate planner users: let me know any tips and tricks you have to stay organized because I ✨need them✨
